{"tid":1581280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"百彈齋主: 點解唔係七千二百萬入面，撥一千萬去對準政權，追討警暴？","createTime":"2019-09-19T13:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:51:59.000Z","uid":7971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd63abf7b291936819cd0576d6d0bd58b895f73","tid":1581280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"百彈齋主: 「點解唔係七千二百萬入面，撥一千萬去對準政權，追討警暴？<br />\n<br />\n無，我問下姐，應該唔算分化吧？」<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】多名於反修例示威中報稱被警員打傷的市民發起眾籌計劃，向警方提出民事訴訟，<span style=\"color: orange;\">首階段眾籌一千萬元為目標</span>。召集人表示，民事訴訟是受害人主動出擊控告警察濫權，希望警方知道即使執行職務時遮蓋職員編號，亦要承擔後果。<br />\n<br />\n過去三個月反修例示威中，警察執法行動引起爭議。6月12日，有巿民在金鐘夏慤道被多名速龍小隊成員打，有人中彈倒地。8月11日，有市民被喬裝警員推到地上，令到左手骨折，其中一個關節位碎成四塊。亦有市民在住所樓下的公園被防暴警員用警棍，打到頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n他們聯同其他受傷的市民發起眾籌，向警方提出民事訴訟，首階段眾籌一千萬元為目標，而民事申索中的賠償會全數交由受害人處理。<br />\n<br />\n至於訴訟方是誰，他們指，要視乎是否可查出施襲的警員身分。<br />\n<br />\n他們表示會視乎首階段眾籌反應，以及日後有沒有更多受害人需要協助，再決定是否繼續次階段的籌款計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=363329&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363329%26refer%3D&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=58e6cfac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363329%26refer%3D&h=f100ecae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=363329&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以解答下？ <br />\n扲7份之1 做一件大家想做嘅事 又唔岩？<br />\n定又有人話個基金用途唔同咗？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>連我個捐咗一舊錢嘅淺黃老母都問 依家個7000萬 做過咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係未可以做翻啲實際野先？錢無咗 唔可以再籌過？</strong>"},{"pid":"2057a542295744bbb97c718957bf07f131179ea3","tid":1581280,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=d901ec7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"bb486597a5bca269bc453f07166fb127018bdf5f","tid":1581280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"Source: 百彈齋主Facebook"},{"pid":"5cd907600bf09a9fc634428f2de4084a8e2d912e","tid":1581280,"uid":7971,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會唔準問基金用途？<br />\n一陣又話分化<br />\n<br />\n但依家真係有需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314f68c129b872cea1a090aa7c135e034df98555","tid":1581280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e5a1562be8e75e15e5bda7ee6c167ad64e3c87b","tid":1581280,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6bb18bdfb3f75c2ffeb9c4c9706f099e597c7cf6","tid":1581280,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"一齊e爆林鄭，去&ldquo;社區對話&rdquo;寧願黃絲入去都唔好俾班維穩五毛入去圍爐！<br />\n<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/had056/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fhad056%2Ftc%2F&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=4907cf0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/had056/tc/</a>"},{"pid":"6ee682cf43fe7250240bc734c4e3289aa9f2756d","tid":1581280,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited